The List of Fields in Current Form frame allows you to create a new field
using the definition of an existing field in the current form that is
being edited.  Move the cursor up/down the displayed list until the
desired field is highlighted.  The list will scroll if there are more
fields than currently displayed.  Choose the `Select' menuitem to create
a new field.

The menu commands are:

        MENU COMMANDS           SYNOPSIS
        -------------           --------

        Select                  The definition of the highlighted field
                                is used as the basis for creating a
                                new field.

        Cancel                  Return to the Layout Frame of Vifred without
                                creating a new field.

        ListForms               Display a list of forms in the database
                                that the user has access to.

        Help                    Access the Ingres Help facility.
